snippet.title: Dumpy & Bumpy Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Join Dumpy & Bumpy in this block pushin', bomb explodin', partner throwin' hectic romp through 50 puzzle stages with 5 uniquely themed worlds!

Out now on itch.io with a FREE DEMO! 
https://programancer.itch.io/dumpy

(Candid Description: I've worked really hard on this game over the past couple of months- I really wanted to make something fun for siblings during the pandemic. I always try to make games that are inspired by and invoke fond memories, and I have lots from playing Bomberman and Bubble Bobble with my brother. I hope I can bring those same kinds of experiences to others as well~)
